CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1778166669
OL,3,CMan who grabbed woman's hair convicted
OL,4,Cin first sex-based harassment
OL,5,Cprosecution
OL,7,F"This first-of-its-kind conviction
OL,8,Fproves that through close
OL,9,Fcollaboration across the criminal
OL,10,Fjustice system, we can deliver
OL,11,Foutcomes like these for more victims
OL,12,Fand build a safer environment for
OL,13,Feveryone to be a part of."
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
